  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00057', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-05', NULL, 'essay', '開設 A 油漆行之甲，某日竊取乙之 10 桶油漆，置放於 A 油漆行販售。
一個月後，不知情之丙向甲購買其中 7桶油漆，並將之使用於丙新購買
之 B屋牆壁。又經三個月，乙發現甲竊取油漆及將部分油漆出售給丙，
以及丙將該油漆使用於 B屋牆壁等情事。試問：乙對甲、丙該如何主張
權利？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d41826a9492", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00058', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-05', NULL, 'essay', '甲移居美國前，將登記其名下之A屋委託好友乙管理。不久，乙死亡，
丙見 A 屋長久無人居住而潛入該屋居住。丙居住 16 年後，甲返國得知
丙居住 A 屋，遂請求丙歸還 A 屋，丙則抗辯甲請求歸還 A 屋之權利已
消滅時效完成，而拒絕歸還 A屋。試問：丙之抗辯是否有理？（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d41826a9492", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00059', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-05', NULL, 'essay', '甲因重病而生命垂危，故以錄音方式作成口授遺囑，並指定乙及丙為見
證人。甲之配偶已過世，並生有二子 A及 B，而甲於遺囑中指定A應繼
分為三分之二，並對其姪子 C遺贈新臺幣300萬元。三個月後甲病情好
轉痊癒，但於口授遺囑完成二年後，甲因車禍死亡。試問：A及C得否
依口授遺囑之內容主張該權利？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d41826a9492", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00060', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-9b7ab1bb', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-05', NULL, 'essay', '甲新購買位於 12 層樓之 A屋，搬家遷入 A屋時，其支付移機費委託乙
將原居住 B屋之三部冷氣機移機裝設至 A屋。然而，因乙之助手丙工作
疏失而未固定好冷氣機，導致其中一部冷氣機從高樓掉落而擊中路過之
上班族丁，丁當場不治死亡。另一位上班族戊，則因閃避掉落之冷氣機
而跌倒，小腿骨折住院治療一個月，而戊之母親己於此一個月間擔任戊
之看護。試問：甲、乙及丙對此冷氣機掉落事件該如何負責？（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9d41826a9492", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0401", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "民法", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "四", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00061', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '英譯中：請將下面這段英文譯成正確、流暢的中文（30 分）
The global issues that we face today can seem overwhelming—too much for
anyperson,anyoneorganization,oranyonegovernmenttotackle.Aswesize
up the global challenges we face—from advancing gender equality to
eliminating poverty—it’s crucial to recognize that these issues do not exist in
silos. For instance, progress we have made on issues related to health and
security are exacerbated by climate change. Only by looking at these
challenges holistically, can we have a better chance at making progress on a
range of issues. Facing different problems in human existence, what can
humans accomplish collectively? That’s where the Sustainable Development
Goals come in, a framework designed by the United Nations for peace and
prosperityforboth peopleand theplanet.', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f30c78d18797", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "英文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "一", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00062', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '中譯英：請將下面這段中文譯成正確、流暢的英文（30 分）
近幾年網紅市場蓬勃，有許多人紛紛開始透過自媒體來開創第二事業，
簡單來說就是一般普羅大眾，皆能透過社群平台發表親身經歷、分享所
見所聞。有專家指出，自媒體是人生最值得的投資，因為可以擁有三個
獲得幸福的要素：自由掌控時間、實現自我價值、創造高收入。然而事
實的真相是：相對於傳統的媒體宣傳，自媒體平台宣傳管道偏窄，也容
易出現被封禁或下架的情況。再者，自媒體創作者需要花費大量時間和
精力來撰寫和推廣作品，時間成本高，往往利潤極其微薄。', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:26:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f30c78d18797", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112130", "c": "101", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "英文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員特種考試司法人員考試、法務部調查局調查人員考試、海岸巡防人員考試、移民行政人員考試、未具擬任職務任用資格取得法官遴選資格考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "judicial", "civil_category": "公證人"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00063', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-112-f9fb6a06', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-06', NULL, 'essay', '英文作文：請根據下面的說明寫一篇約 250-300字的英文作文（40 分）
